c:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Krisp and Suno share a solid foundation of core features including . Where Krisp pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Speech To Text and Noise Removal and Real Time, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Suno uniquely offers Music Generation and Multilingual, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Krisp holds an overall score of 8/10 and an ease of use score of 9/10, while Suno scores 8/10 overall and 10/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
d:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both platforms start at similar price points ($8/mo). Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Krisp's free tier and Suno's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
